imilar to the\nvertical mixing time in the troposphere. This process is thus likely\nresponsible for the o-p equilibration of H$_2$ in the mid-troposphere implied\nby CIRS measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2019 16:21:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-24"}
