 galaxies. We suggest that the solution may instead\nreside in revisions to stellar wind predictions, softer X-ray sources, or very\nhot products of binary evolution at low metallicity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2019 18:58:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 31 May 2020 08:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-02"}
