ed to alter particle deposition patterns during evaporation-based fabrication\ntechniques and ink-jet printing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Sep 2019 15:08:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 17:44:12 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 5 Dec 2019 14:42:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-17"}
