 dynamics and quenching the oscillations at high currents. The\nresults are in good agreement with our experimental data published elsewhere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Sep 2019 15:08:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
